Ward {2}
Compete [i](You get a score counter once on each of your turns when you attack. Spend three score counters as a sorcery to create Trophy tokens.)[/i]
At the beginning of your end step, you lose 1 life and draw a card. If you control a Trophy, instead you draw a card and each opponent loses 2 life and you gain 2 life.
